quran[96]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,"Si Darngal ngal darorii ko feere mun alaa."
  56,2,"Alanaa wonkii woo fennugol ngal, wano ɓe fenniraynoo ngal ka aduna."
  56,3,"Hoyfinɗinirayngal heeferɓe bomɓe ɓen naadeede Yiite, ngal ɓamtira fii gomɗimɓe ɓen naadugol Aljanna."
  56,4,"Si leydi ndin dilliniroyaama dillannde mawnde."
  56,5,"Pelle ɗen ɗigginiroyee ɗigginannde."
  56,6,"ɗe wontira nden muncannde ɗon, collaari sariindi ndi tabitataa."
  56,7,"Wontoyon nooneeji tati, nden ñalnde:"
  56,8,"Ko wontirooɓe ñaamo ɓen henndorayɓe talki mun ɗin ka ñaamo. Iskin toowal e mawngu martaba maɓɓe !"
  56,9,"E wontirooɓe nano ɓen henndorayɓe talki mun ɗin ka nano. Bone bis e ɓen yimɓe nano !"
  56,10,"Ko adondiraynooɓe ɓen e golle moƴƴe ka aduna, woni ko adoytee naadeede Aljanna ka laakara."
  56,11,"Ko ɓen woni ɓadnitaaɓe ɓen ka Allah."
  56,12,"Hiɓe e nder Aljannaaji neeminiiɗi, ka ɓe dakmitora kala noone neema."
  56,13,"Dental jeyaangal e ɗee mofte, e mofte adinooɓe ɓen."
  56,14,"E yimɓe seeɗaaɓe, jeyaaɓe e mofte sakkitiiɓe ɓen, ɓen kadi ko adinooɓe ɓallinaaɓe."
  56,15,"Hiɓe e hoore danɗe yuɓɓiraaɗe kaŋŋe."
  56,16,"Hara hiɓe soɓɓindii e ɗen danɗe, ɓe fewtondiri, tawa ɓe runtandirtaa."
  56,17,"Sukaaɓe duuminaaɓe hino wanngoo hakkunde maɓɓe, ko ligganoo ɓe, ɓen nawyataa ɓe lannataa."
  56,18,"Hara hiɓe jinndida ton e ñedduɗe ɗe alaa uddooɗe, e caltale uddotooɗe, e koroy hebbiniraakoy beere ilaynde nder Aljanna nde taƴondirtaa."
  56,19,"Nden wa'aa wa beere aduna nden, tawde mo yarii nde o muusetaake hoore o haangataake."
  56,20,"Ɓen sukaaɓe wanngodato hakkunde maɓɓe ton kadi e muuyanteeɗi ɗi ɓe suɓotoo."
  56,21,"Ɓe jinndida ton kadi e teewu colli ngu ɓe tuuyatee."
  56,22,"Hino woodani ɓe ka Aljanna ton kadi, rewɓe labaaɓe yooɗa e yaaja giteeɓe"
  56,23,"Wa'uɓe wa kaŋŋe lu'ulu'u reenaaɗe nder oogirɗe."
  56,24,"Ɗum ko njoɓdi golle maɓɓe moƴƴe ɗen aduna."
  56,25,"Ɓe nanataa ka nder Aljanna ton, haala bonuka, wanaa ko fawata jom mun bakkaat."
  56,26,"Ɓe nanataa ton si wanaa ko Malaa'ika'en saɗnata ɓe kon, e ko ɓe salmondirta hakkonde maɓɓe kon."
  56,27,"E joman en ñaame tottirteeɓe ɗeri mum en juuɗe ñaame, alah ko ɓuri mawnude ɓe daraja e ngonko ka Alla."
  56,28,"Ɓe wonoyay e leɗɗe ɗe alaa bulle-gi*e-, ɗe lorrataa."
  56,29,"E banaanaaje sukuɗe, weertiraaɗe yoga e dow yoga."
  56,30,"E ɗowdi duumiindi, ɗi iwataa."
  56,31,"E ndiyam juurayɗam, ɗam taƴondirtaa."
  56,32,"E ɓiɗɓe leɗɗe ɗuuɗuɗe ko limotaako."
  56,33,"Ɗe taƴondirantaaɓe fes, ɗe alaa yonta, huunde kadi toŋataa ɗe."
  56,34,"Ɓe wonay e leecee toownaaɗe e hoore danɗe."
  56,35,"Ko Menen woni ko tagi ɓen huurul'ayniiɓe fuɗɗi ɓe."
  56,36,"Men waɗi ɓe curbaaɓe ɓe yiidaali e gorko."
  56,37,"Rewɓe yiɗuɓe moodiiɓe mun, goreeɓe."
  56,38,"Men tagir ɓen, fii yimɓe ñaamo ɓen, maande maloore maɓɓe nden."
  56,39,"Ɓen ko dental jeyaaɓe e mofte Annabaaɓe adinooɓe ɓen."
  56,40,"E seeɗaaɓe jeyaaɓe e mofte Annabiijo Muhammadu ɗen (yo o his) mofte sakkitiiɓe ɓen."
  56,41,"E jom en nane tottirteeɓe ɗeri mum en e nane mum en ndaw ko boni alhaaleeji e battane."
  56,42,"Ɓen no e henndu tiiɗundu nguleeki, e ndiyam tiiɗuɗam fatugol."
  56,43,"E ɗowdi iwndi e curki ɓawluki."
  56,44,"Wanaa henndu ɓuuɓundu, wanaa labaandu yi*annde."
  56,45,"Ado ɓe wonnde e ɗee lepte maɓɓe, hari ko ɓe neeminanooɓe aduna, ɓe alaano himme si wanaa tuuyooji maɓɓe."
  56,46,"Ɓe laatino hiɓe haɓɓitoo e yeddugol Allah, rewa sanamu ko woori Mo."
  56,47,"Hari hiɓe yeddaynoo ummital, ɓe jalkita fii maggal ɓe wi'a: Enee, hara si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ƴi'e kiɗɗe, hara men wuurnitete ɓaawo ɗum?"
  56,48,"Hay baabiraaɓe amen adinooɓe men kadi ɓen maayude immintinoyte?"
  56,49,"An Nulaaɗo, maakan ɓee fennuɓe fii ummital : Pellet, yimɓe adinooɓe e sakkitiiɓe fow e mun."
  56,50,"Ko on mooɓoyteeɓe Ñalnde Darngal feere mun alaa, fii ñaaweede yoɓitee."
  56,51,"Refti onon fennooɓe ummital majjuɓe laawol poocingol ko ñaamooɓe ñande darnga e ɓesnaaɗe lekki Jaqquum ko kiin ɓuri bonde e soɓde ɓesnaaɗe."
  56,52,""
  56,53,"Leggal ngal hebbiiroyton dimɗe mun haaɗuɗe, deedi mon yeewuɗi."
  56,54,"Surkoron ngal ndiyam wulɗam haa fati."
  56,55,"On ɗuɗɗiniroyay yarugol e maggal, wano ngelooba ɗuɗɗinirta yarugol si ñawii."
  56,56,"Ko on ñaametee mettuɗo e ndiyam haaɗuɗo, woni ko ɓe jaɓɓortee ñalnde njoɓdi kuuɗe mon."
  56,57,"Ko Menen tagi on, onon yo fennuɓe ummital, hari on woodaaka. Ko haɗi on goonginnde wonnde Men wuurnitay on si on maayii?"
  56,58,"Onon ɓee yimɓe, on yi'ii maniiyu mo rufoton on e rennga rewɓe ɓen?"
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata on maniiyu? Kaa ko Menen woni tagooɓe mo?"
  56,60,"Ko Menen woni ko hoddiri maayde nden hakkunde mon; gooto kala e lajal, aditotaako wattintaako. Men wonaali ronkiteeɓe."
  56,61,"E wattitugol honooɓe mon e tagudu e mbaadi mon, Men fuɗɗira on e ko on anndaano e tagudu e mbaadi."
  56,62,"Gomɗii hiɗon anndi no Men tagiri on non ka aranun. E on taskotaako anndon wonnde taguɗo On aranun ɗum, hino hattani immintingol on si on maayii?"
  56,63,"On yi'ii gabbe ɗe sankoton ɗen ka leydi?"
  56,64,"Ko onon fuɗinta ɗen gabbe? Kaa ko Menen?"
  56,65,"Si Men haajuno waɗugol ndun remuru foron, ko pellet, Men wattayno mo ɗum, fewndo ka ɓadini ƴoƴugol. Wattinon ɓaawo ɗum, hiɗon ŋalɗa e ko heɓu ngu."
  56,66,"Wi'on : Menen ko men leptiraaɓe hayrugol ko men nafqi kon."
  56,67,"Wurin ko men haaaɓe arsike."
  56,68,"On yi'ii ndiyam ɗam yaroton ɗam si on ɗomɗaama?"
  56,69,"E ko onon saaƴiniri ɗam ka kammu? Kaa ko Menen saaƴini ɗam?"
  56,70,"Si Men haajuno waɗugol ɗam ndiyam ɗuuɗuɗam lamɗam, hara ɗam nafataa yarugol wanaa yarnirgol, ko pellet, Men waɗayno ɗum. Ko haɗi on yettugol Allah e ko O jippiniri yurmeende Makko nden kon, ndiyam welɗam?"
  56,71,"On yi'ii yiite nge huɓɓirton haajuuji mon ɗin?"
  56,72,"E ko onon tagi leɗɗe huɓɓirteeɗe ngen yiite? Kaa ko Menen tagiri ɗe yurmegol on?"
  56,73,"Men waɗir ngee yiite ko waajitoron Yiite laakara ngen, e nafitor nge setotooɓe mon."
  56,74,"Subbunhinor an Nulaaɗo, Joomi maa, Mawnuɗo e ko O hanndaa e mun."
  56,75,"Allah woondirii nokkuuli koode ɗen."
  56,76,"Ko pellet, woondirgol mutirɗe ɗee koode, ko mawɗum, si ɗon anndunoo. Tawde maandeeji e tasakuyeeji no ton ko lannataa."
  56,77,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare wonaande janngeede e mon, ko Alqur'aanaare teddunde. Tawde hinde ɗuuɗi nafooje mawɗe."
  56,78,"Wonnde e deftere reenaande e gite yimɓe, nden woni Alluwal reenaangal ngal."
  56,79,"Meemataa nden, si wanaa Malaa'ika'en laɓɓinaa e bakkatuuji e ayiibe."
  56,80,"Ko jippiniraande ka Jeyɗo tageefo ngon, e dow Annabiijo Muhammadu jom kisiyee."
  56,81,"E ko ndee yewtere woni ko fennoton, onon ɓee sirkooɓe fennoobe?"
  56,82,"Hiɗon waɗira yettirgol mon Allah ngol e ko O arsikiri on neema, fennugol on ɗum? Wonon e dammbirgol toɓo ngon battinorgol hoodere (naw`u) nden? Wi'on: Men toɓinorii hoodere naw'u kaariiree e kaariire?"
  56,83,"Ko haɗata si ruuhu on yottike ka lookoƴere,"
  56,84,"Hara onon hiɗon ndaara ngirɓoowo on fewndo yeeso mon on tuma."
  56,85,"Hara non ko Menen e ganndal e kattal Amen, wonndude e Malaa'ka'en Amen, ɓuri on ɓadaade maayoowo mon on, ko woni tun, on yi'ataa ɓen Malaa'ikaaɓe."
  56,86,"Ko haɗata on, si tawiino hara ko no aaƴoriɗon non, wonnde on immintintaake fii warjeede golle mon,"
  56,87,"Rutton kin wonkii wonuki yaltude e maayoowo mon on, si tawii ko on goonguɓe? On hattanaa ɗum."
  56,88,"Si tawii on maayɗo ko jeyaaɗo e adondirtenooɓe e moƴƴuɗi."
  56,89,"Haray ko fowtere nde jokkondirtaa e ronkere alah caggal mum, e arsike laaɓuɗo, e yurmeende, e Aljanna mo o neeminotoo e mun kala ko wonkii makko faaletee, woni ko woodani mo."
  56,90,"Si tawii maayɗo on ko jeyaaɗo e yimɓe ñaamo ɓen, haray wata fii makko sunin; tawde ko kisal e hoolaare woodani ɓen."
  56,91,""
  56,92,"Si tawii non maayɗo on ko jeyanooɗo e fennunooɓe ko Nulaaɗo on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun on, majjunooɓe laawol focciingol ngol."
  56,93,"Haray jipporde makko nde o jaɓɓetee e mun nden, ko ndiyam fatayɗam."
  56,94,"E sumoyeede Yiite Jahiimi ngen."
  56,95,"Pellet, ko Men fillani maa kon an Nulaaɗo, ko goonga yananaaɗo, mo sikke alaa e mu'un."
  56,96,"Senin innde Joomi maa Mawɗo On, mawninaa Mo e kala ustaare!"
